WEBVTT

00:06:25.080 --> 00:06:30.936
This is the biggest global wave
of migration since the Second World War,

00:06:30.960 --> 00:06:32.720
and it's only set to grow.

00:06:34.080 --> 00:06:35.440
So far this year,

00:06:36.160 --> 00:06:40.256
more that 2,100 migrants
have lost their lives

00:06:40.280 --> 00:06:41.880
on their way to Europe.

